# trusted_hosts
# =============
# One regex per line for posting/injection hosts that may receive selected
# bypasses.  Trust narrowly and never assume this disables binary, size, or
# crosspost checks unless the matching trusted_bypass_* option explicitly says
# so.
#
# Exact host:
# ^faq-poster\.example\.net$
#
# Numbered, administratively controlled posting cluster:
# ^faq-poster[0-9]+\.example\.net$
#
# Two exact infrastructure addresses:
# ^(?:192\.0\.2\.10|192\.0\.2\.11)$
